Polyphony Options for TASCAM 4x4HR USB audio card on linux

This utility uses libusb-1.0 to setup the TASCAM 4x4HR options via USB control trasfers.

You may need following packages installed: libusb-1.0-0, libusb-1.0-0-dev 

Example:

#set ports to mono:
./potascam --stereo-mode12 0
./potascam --stereo-mode34 0

#disable loopback mode
./potascam --disable-loopback

#enable inputs:
./potascam --enable-input 1
./potascam --enable-input 2
./potascam --enable-input 3
./potascam --enable-input 4

#set outputs to computer output
./potascam --lineout12
./potascam --lineout34
